----------------------------------------------------------

One Year Ago: Yahoo! Taps Into Online Banking
(Posted 28-Jul-00)

As analysts have recently pointed out, leading portal
site Yahoo! (Nasdaq: YHOO) has no problem getting
people to come to its site.  Now Yahoo! is working
toward getting its visitors to stay awhile.  Today,
Yahoo! announced a deal with online bank Telebank
(Nasdaq: TBFC) that will allow Telebank customers
to view their account information on Yahoo!...

See The Full Story:
http://www.ecommercetimes.com/news/articles2000/000728-tc.shtml

